commentTextItems.html: Vaas to Astle, down the leg side, Astle drives off the back foot, 2 runs, fielded by Maharoof

commentPostTextItems.html: New Zealand wins this match comperhesively and secure the series with lead of 3-0. Nathan Astle batted brillantly through out the innigns and he had quite lucky to dismissed twice in a no balls. That is it from us, please join with us January 6th for the 3rd ODI between this two team played at Napier.

Vaas to Astle, good line and length delivery, Astle drives through the on side, 1 run, fielded by Maharoof
(no ball) Vaas to Astle, Astle plays a pull-shot, 4 runs
Vaas to Astle, wide of off stump, Astle plays a pull-shot, 6 runs
(no ball) Vaas to Astle, no runs, bowled of a no ball! slower delivery on the stumps, Astle pulls across the line, inside edge into the pads and middle stump uprooted
Vaas to Astle, good length but wide of the off stump, Astle drives it away, no runs, fielded by Dilshan
Fernando to Astle, wide outside the off stump, Astle driving, 1 run, fielded by Muralitharan
